text: U ji koceren ereban (ewa desta ku ne cubune qirina Tebuke) ji bona ku ji wan ra destur be dane (ewan ji di mala xwe da weki wane para da mane, runen) hinek sedem ji bona xwe ra (hunandine) hatine (ji bo ku tu ewan bibaxisini). Le ewane ku Yezdan u Pexembere Wi dabune derewderandine hene! Ewan runistibune, qe (ji bona baxisandina xwe) ne hatibune, ewane file ne ji wan hene! We di nezik da sapateke dilsoz bi wan da were
